name: Beauty & Brillo 003 Coral
description: Meet a Coral. Afrobeat and beach party lover. Enjoy the heat and the shrimp cocktail (aka rompe colchón). The swing of the hammock while looking at the sky makes her wonder in what physical spaces we can coincide with our past lives. One day walking along the beach, he found a turtle that had just been born and helped it to enter its first marine journey, since then he has only thought on which other shore that little being will have ended up. There's no beauty without some warm brillo.
